### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pawan Kumar",
  "email": "pawan7@gmail.com",
  "password": "pawan@45678"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pawan7@gmail.com",
  "password": "pawan@45678"
}

